  a  number  of  special  initiatives  have  been taken to change the lives of farmers under the leadership of honble prime minister shri  narendra  modi  irrigation  facility  has  improved  availability  of  seeds  and fertilizers  has  been  ensured  target  has  been  set  for  improving  the  farm productivity  by  issuing soil  health  card  per  drop  more corp scheme  has  been launched  it  is  the  intention  of  the  honble  prime  minister  to  make  meaningful efforts for doubling the income of the farmers   